{"an5.244:0.1":"Anguttara Nikaya 5.244 ","an5.244:0.2":"25. Duccaritavagga ","an5.244:0.3":"Pathamamanoduccaritasutta ","an5.244:1.1":"“Pancime, bhikkhave, adinava manoduccarite …pe… anisamsa manosucarite. ","an5.244:1.2":"Katame panca? ","an5.244:1.3":"Attapi attanam na upavadati; ","an5.244:1.4":"anuvicca vinnu pasamsanti; ","an5.244:1.5":"kalyano kittisaddo abbhuggacchati; ","an5.244:1.6":"asammulho kalam karoti; ","an5.244:1.7":"kayassa bheda param marana sugatim saggam lokam upapajjati. ","an5.244:1.8":"Ime kho, bhikkhave, panca anisamsa manosucarite”ti. ","an5.244:1.9":"Catuttham. "}